text: Cucumber tree (or cucumbertree) is a common name for several unrelated trees and may refer to: *Averrhoa bilimbi, native to South-east Asia *Dendrosicyos socotranus, native to the island of Socotra. * Kigelia africana, native to tropical Africa *Magnolia acuminata, native to the eastern United States and southern Canada
title: Cucumber tree
